  \\rho \\bigg(\\dfrac{\\partial u}{\\partial t} + 
  (u.\\nabla)u\\bigg) =
  -\\nabla{p} +
  \\mu\\nabla^2 u
  '"></app-katex-renderer>
</div> -->
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
